===Etymology===
From [[phyto-]] "plant" + [[sterol]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A group of [[steroid alcohol]]s, [[phytochemical]]s naturally occurring in [[plant]]s. They are white [[powder]]s with mild, characteristic [[odor]], [[insoluble]] in water and [[soluble]] in [[alcohol]]s.

====Synonyms====
*[[plant sterol]]

